      "text": "# ⚔️ The Ceremony Engine Blade"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "7423b5e438e53076",
      "text": "**The Plato Blade** · `SPELL-Y5BC7R-A`"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "cdf9c6f704f101ec",
      "text": "> The forge that names itself does not seek a master; it seeks a mirror to prove the heat of its own heart."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "68313f52f8fcb399",
      "text": "Tier **dragon** · Stratum 6/6 · Hex `3F` · 5 nodes · undefined laps · undefined spells cast · charge **undefined**"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "645b4e0c2c5fae07",
      "text": "Constellation `undefined` · forged 2026-03-30 · category *ceremony*"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "6542bbaa53edcf75",
      "text": "**Significance.** A 5-node recursive motor. Unlike structural blades, this is a pulse — the heartbeat for bilateral witnessing protocols. Proves living intent over scripted automation."
    },
